  "title": "A round gray and red UFO hovered at low altitude in Curitiba [2001]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/13/a-round-gray-and-red-ufo-hovered-at-low-altitude-in-curitiba-2001/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-na",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>MARCH 11th, 2001</strong>. Time: 19h15pm. Duration: 15 minutes. In the neighborhood of Guabirotuba, in Curitiba, State of Paraná, a witness spotted a round gray and red UFO, hovering at about 45 meters of altitude. According to the sighting report, the object remained stationary during the fifteen minutes it was sighted, leaving no trace of condensation. The reported event was observed under good visibility conditions, in a cloudless sky. There was no record of electrical and electronic interference during the sighting.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.600. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre avistamento de ovni no bairro de Guabirotuba, em Curitiba, Estado do Paraná”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>MARCH 11th, 2001. Time: 19h15pm. Duration: 15 minutes. In the neighborhood of Guabirotuba, in Curitiba, State of Paraná, a witness spotted a round gray and red UFO, hovering at about 45 meters of altitude. According to the sighting report, the object remained stationary during the fifteen minutes it was sighted, leaving no trace of condensation. [&hellip;]</p>\n",
